    "Emerging factors within the anticipation sentiment were the transformative aspect of ChatGPT.",
    "One faculty called it a \"harbinger of a tectonic transformation of almost all aspects of academia\".",
    "Other factors for anticipation were ChatGPT's added value and inclusivity, with faculty calling for higher education to harness AI and think about how machine learning can improve learning and teaching processes.",
    "Faculty tweeted about how ChatGPT can renew and energize discussions about changing assessments, teaching academic integrity, and supporting student use in a career context.",
    "The anticipation of ChatGPT reflects frequently touted benefits of the AI, but also points to the potential of this innovation becoming driven by student needs (Dai et al., 2023)."
